      "text": "想象一个旋转编码器，正在读取转轴的角度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "如果用普通二进制，从 3 转到 4 时，三位要同时翻转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "各位的翻转很难完全同步，一瞬间可能读出错误的乱码。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "格雷码正是为解决这个难题而生的一种巧妙编码。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "adjacent",
      "line_id": "adj-2",
      "filename": "adjacent-adj-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/adjacent-adj-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "这样从一个数跳到下一个数，永远只翻转一个比特。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "convert",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
      "filename": "convert-conv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/convert-conv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "写成公式就是，格雷码等于 n 异或 n 右移一位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "karnaugh",
      "line_id": "kar-2",
      "filename": "karnaugh-kar-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gray-code/yunxi/karnaugh-kar-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "因为相邻格只差一位，相邻的一才能合并化简逻辑表达式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gray-code",
      "section_id": "interaction",
